text: Waited 45min for food despite ordering early at 5:41pm. Service staff did not have courtesy to pre-empt me about the long waiting time. Food was average. Hair in Kang Kong.  Avoid at all cost.
Service is good, prompt and friendly. We love the food too as we tried the mothers day menu, entire family loves this too will be back !

Took over the space previously run by Hong Kong Street 香港街zi char stall. Even though I prefer the previous stall's menu, I am thankful that Kimly can prepare meatfree meals too. Ordered their 罗汉斋 Lohanzhai stir-fried vegetables rice set. Not too heavily seasoned, simple food with real (no mock meat) ingredients, which I prefer.

Moved out of Joo Seng 3 years ago but i had a chance to be back in the area. This zhi char was a far cry from 136 zhi char back then
I ordered the scallion pork rice & pork ribs rice
Both were sub par as compared to the old zhi char stall
Food not make it try it yourself n review don't how to describe bad
